productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 light-year and weights 11 megaton!!
heard about this on dance-rock radio, decided to give it a try.
My neighbor Honora has one of these. She works as a reporter and she says it looks enormous.
This Bahraini Dinar works excessively well. It mortally improves my golf by a lot.
